scopes.name: schedule_only
scopes.explanation: Lines 0-167 comprise the entire Schedule to the ISDA Master Agreement, including all its Parts (1-5) and the signature blocks. There is no indication of standard pre-print, CSA annexes, or other sections outside the Schedule in the provided text. The Schedule begins at line 0 ('SCHEDULE') and ends at the execution/signature lines. All content is relevant to the user's request to filter the Schedule.
